  <thing id="mTowerStl" name="Tower Shield, Steel" description="This shield is identical to the tower shield described on page 125 of the Player&#146;s Handbook, except that it is made of steel and therefore responds differently to special attacks such as {i}warp wood{/i} and {i}heat metal{/i}. Characters proficient with the normal (wooden) tower shield are also automatically proficient with the steel tower shield.\n\nWhen employing a tower shield in combat, you take a -2 penalty on attack rolls." compset="Armor">
