  <thing id="fAuspMark" name="Auspicious Marking" description="Goliaths place great stock in how the mottled variations in skin pigmentation herald events in that goliath&#146;s future. Your skin patterns indicate that fate has marked you for greatness, and the patterns shift slowly to take new forms.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Goliath.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Goliaths who can see your skin pattern are subconsciously affected by it. You gain a +2 bonus on all Charisma-based skill checks when dealing with other goliaths. In addition, you can reroll any stabilization check once per turn." compset="Feat" summary="+2 to Cha based skills vs Goliaths, reroll stabilization checks once per round." uniqueness="useronce">
