  <thing id="fBurFriend" name="Burrow Friend" description="Your natural rapport with burrowing mammals improves.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Gnome, Cha 13.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain a +2 bonus on Handle Animal checks and wild empathy checks involving burrowing mammals.\n\nIf you have the spell-like ability to speak with burrowing mammals, you can use this ability one extra time per day per point of Charisma bonus.\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: Gnomes can normally use {i}speak with animals{/i} to converse with burrowing animals only once per day." compset="Feat" summary="+2 to Handle Animal and wild empathy vs burrowing mammals." uniqueness="useronce">
