  <thing id="fDeflArmor" name="Deflective Armor" description="Your armor shields you from touch attacks as well as regular blows.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Heavy Armor Optimization.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: While you are psionically focused and wearing heavy armor, the AC bonus from your armor (including any enhancement bonuses) applies against touch attacks as well as regular attacks." compset="Feat" summary="Heavy armor&apos;s AC bon applies vs touch att while psionically focused." uniqueness="useronce">
