  <thing id="fDivDamRed" name="Divine Damage Reduction" description="You can channel energy to give yourself a small amount of protection from weapons.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Con 13, Wis 13, Earth Sense, Earth&#146;s Warding, ability to rebuke earth creatures.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As a standard action, you can spend one of your rebuke earth creatures attempts to give yourself damage reduction 2/adamantine. This benefit lasts for a number of rounds equal to your character level. You must be touching the ground to use this feat." compset="Feat" summary="Standard, use 1 rebuke earth as touch ground to gain DR 2/adamantine for X rds." uniqueness="useronce">
