  <thing id="fDivSplShl" name="Divine Spellshield" description="You can channel energy to help your allies resist spells and spell-like effects.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Ability to rebuke earth creatures, racial bonus on saves against spells.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As a standard action, you can spend one of your rebuke earth creatures attempts to grant all allies within 30 feet a +2 sacred bonus on saving throws against spells and spell-like effects. This bonus lasts for a number of rounds equal to your character level. You must be touching the ground to use this feat." compset="Feat" summary="Stand, use 1 rebuke earth to give allies in 30 ft +2 sac bon to save vs spl for X rds." uniqueness="useronce">
