  <thing id="fEarPower" name="Earth Power" description="You draw psionic energy from raw stone.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Con 13, Wis 13, Earth Sense.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you are psionically focused and standing on stone or unworked earth (including normal soil), you can pull psychic energy from the earth when you manifest a power. When you manifest a power in this way, you pay 1 less power point than you normally would. The use of this feat cannot reduce a power&#146;s cost below 1 power point.\n\nYou cannot use this ability when you expend your psionic focus to enhance the same power in a different manner. For example, if you have the Maximize Power feat, you cannot expend your focus to maximize a power and also reduce the cost of that same power." compset="Feat" summary="On stone/unworked earth pay 1 less PP (minimum 1), can&apos;t use when expend focus." uniqueness="useronce">
