  <thing id="fEarthWard" name="Earth Warding" description="You can channel energy to infuse your skin with the strength of the earth.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Con 13, Wis 13, Earth Sense, ability to rebuke earth creatures.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As a standard action, spend one of your rebuke earth creatures attempts to increase your natural armor bonus by 2. This increase lasts for a number of minutes equal to your Constitution bonus.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You must be touching the ground to use this feat." compset="Feat" summary="Stand, use 1 rebuke earth while touch ground to gain +2 nat armor for X min." uniqueness="useronce">
