  <thing id="fEnchSonge" name="Enchanting Song" description="You can channel the power of your bardic music to temporarily increase the power of your enchantment spells.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Perform (any one) 5 ranks, Spell Focus (enchantment), bardic music.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As you cast a spell of the enchantment school, you may spend one daily use of your bardic music ability to increase the caster level and saving throw DC of that spell by 1. These bonuses stack with those provided by other feats, such as Spell Focus." compset="Feat" summary="Free, use 1 music to add +1 to DC and CL of enchantment spell." uniqueness="useronce">
