  <thing id="fExtraSil" name="Extra Silence" description="You can generate a field of silence more often than other whisper gnomes can.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Whisper gnome.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can use your racial {i}silence{/i} spell-like ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Charisma bonus.\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: A whisper gnome can normally use his {i}silence{/i} spell-like ability once per day.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You can take this feat more than once. Each time you take it after the first, you gain three additional uses of your {i}silence{/i} ability per day." compset="Feat">
