  <thing id="fFocusShl" name="Focused Shield" description="Your mental focus makes you more adept at using your shield.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Shield Proficiency.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: While you are psionically focused and holding a ready shield with which you are proficient, the AC bonus provided by your shield increases by 1." compset="Feat" summary="If psionically focused and readied shield, +1 to shield&apos;s AC bon." uniqueness="useronce">
