  <thing id="fGnoFoe" name="Gnome Foe" description="Your battle techniques against your racial foes improve.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Gnome.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain a +2 racial bonus on weapon damage rolls against kobolds and goblinoids (including goblins, hobgoblins, and bugbears)." compset="Feat" summary="+2 racial bon to weapon damage vs kobolds and goblinoids." uniqueness="useronce">
