  <thing id="fGrHArmOpt" name="Greater Heavy Armor Optimization" description="You have mastered the use of heavy armor, maximizing its protective qualities while moving more easily in it.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Armor Proficiency (heavy), Heavy Armor Optimization, base attack bonus +8.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: When you are wearing heavy armor, lessen the armor check penalty of the armor by 2 and increase the armor bonus by 1. Both of these effects stack with the benefit of the Heavy Armor Optimization feat, for a total lessening of the armor check penalty by 3 and a total increase to the armor bonus of 2.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: A fighter may select Greater Heavy Armor Optimization as one of her fighter bonus feats (see page 38 of the Player&#146;s Handbook)." compset="Feat" summary="When wear heavy armor, -3 armor check penalty, +2 bon to AC." uniqueness="useronce">
