  <thing id="fHvyArmOpt" name="Heavy Armor Optimization" description="You have trained extensively in heavy armor, and you have learned to take advantage of the protection it offers.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Armor Proficiency (heavy), base attack bonus +4.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: When you are wearing heavy armor, lessen the armor check penalty of the armor by 1 and increase the armor bonus by 1.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: A fighter may select Heavy Armor Optimization as one of his fighter bonus feats." compset="Feat" summary="When wearing heavy armor, decrease ACP by 1, increase armor bonus by 1." uniqueness="useronce">
