  <thing id="fImpRockHu" name="Improved Rock Hurling" description="Your accuracy and effectiveness with thrown rocks improves.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Str 23, Rock Hurling, size Large or larger (goliaths qualify by virtue of their powerful build racial trait).\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can hurl rocks weighing 40 to 50 pounds (Small objects) with a range increment of 80 feet. The rocks deal 2d6 points of damage plus your Strength modifier. Rocks have a maximum range of five range increments. Additionally, you gain a +1 bonus on attack rolls when throwing rocks." compset="Feat" summary="May hurl 40-50 lb rocks with a range inc 80 ft &amp; 2d6 dam, +1 to att when throw rocks." uniqueness="useronce">
