  <thing id="fMarkBless" name="Markings of the Blessed" description="Your skin markings shift into a pattern that resists a wide array of harmful effects in times of trouble.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Goliath, Auspicious Marking.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Up to three times per day, you can roll a second d20 when attempting any saving throw and use either of the two results." compset="Feat" summary="3/day, roll two d20 for a save and use either." uniqueness="useronce">
