  <thing id="fPiercDark" name="Pierce the Darkness" description="You can channel positive energy to temporarily increase the range of your darkvision.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Ability to turn undead, darkvision.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As a standard action, spend one of your turn undead attempts to double the range of your darkvision. This increase lasts for a number of minutes equal to your character level." compset="Feat" summary="Standard, use 1 turn to double the range of your darkvision for X min." uniqueness="useronce">
