  <thing id="fPierSight" name="Piercing Sight" description="Your fundamental familiarity with illusions allows you to better recognize them.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Gnome.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain a +4 bonus on saving throws made to disbelieve illusions (any illusion spell or effect with &#147;disbelief&#148; in the saving throw entry)." compset="Feat" summary="+4 bon to saves made to disbelieve illusions." uniqueness="useronce">
