  <thing id="fSteadyCon" name="Steady Concentration" description="You are an expert at avoiding distractions and focusing your mind, and you can concentrate clearly even in the most stressful conditions.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Concentration 8 ranks.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can always take 10 on Concentration checks, even when conditions would not normally allow you to do so.\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: A character cannot take 10 on any skill check if distracted or threatened, such as during combat." compset="Feat" summary="You may take 10 on Concentration checks even when distracted/threatened." uniqueness="useronce">
