  <thing id="fStoneback" name="Stoneback" description="You have studied the techniques of fighting underground, and you can protect yourself from the dangers of multiple attackers whenever you can put your back to a solid wall.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Shield Proficiency, Tunnel Fighting.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: If you have a ready shield with which you are proficient and one side of your space is entirely in contact with a solid wall, you cannot be flanked.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: A fighter may select Stoneback as one of his fighter bonus feats (see page 38 of the Player&#146;s Handbook)." compset="Feat" summary="If you have ready shield &amp; one side of space contacts a wall, imm to flank." uniqueness="useronce">
