  <thing id="fTunnelFig" name="Tunnel Fighting" description="You are adept at maneuvering and fighting in tight spaces and underground passages.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Base attack bonus +1.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You do not take a penalty on your attack rolls or to Armor Class when squeezing into or through a tight space.\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: Each movement into or through a narrow space counts as if it were 2 squares, and while squeezed in a narrow space a character takes a &#150;4 penalty on attack rolls and a &#150;4 penalty to AC. See page 148 of the Player&#146;s Handbook for more information on squeezing through tight spaces.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: A fighter may select Tunnel Fighting as one of his fighter bonus feats (see page 38 of the Player&#146;s Handbook)." compset="Feat" summary="You take no penalty to AC or attacks while squeezing through tight spaces." uniqueness="useronce">
