  <thing id="fTurtlDart" name="Turtle Dart" description="You have mastered the style of fighting with a short sword while wearing extremely heavy armor and carrying a large shield.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Exotic Armor Proficiency (battle plate or mountain plate), Exotic Shield Proficiency (extreme shield) or Tower Shield Proficiency, Weapon Focus (short sword).\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: To gain the benefit of this feat, you must be wearing exotic heavy armor and carrying an extreme shield or tower shield. When using this style, you do not provoke attacks of opportunity for moving away from any creature that you attack with your short sword in the same round." compset="Feat" summary="If in exotic hvy armor &amp; extreme/tower shl, no AoO from attacked foe if move." uniqueness="useronce">
