    </thing>
  <thing id="xAcclimate" name="Acclimated" description="Goliaths are automatically acclimated to life at high altitude. They don&#146;t take the penalties for altitude described in the Mountain Travel section on page 90 of the Dungeon Master&#146;s Guide. Unlike other denizens of the mountains, goliaths don&#146;t lose their acclimation to high altitude even if they spend a long time at a lower elevation." compset="Special" summary="Always acclimated to high altitudes, never lost.">
    <usesource source="srcRoS"/>
