  <thing id="cDCHamSpec" name="Hammer Specialist" description="A dwarf cleric&#146;s dedication to the forge-god results in exceptional skill with the warhammer. A dwarf cleric who takes the 4th-level racial substitution level gains the Martial Weapon Proficiency (warhammer) feat (if she doesn&#146;t already have it). She also gains a +2 bonus on damage rolls when wielding a warhammer in melee." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain proficiency with warhammers and a +2 bonus to damage when using them.">
