  <thing id="cDCEarthSP" name="Earthen Spell Power" description="A dwarf cleric who takes the 8th-level racial substitution level draws power from the earth when casting certain spells. When she is in contact with the ground, the cleric&#146;s effective caster level when casting spells with the earth descriptor (or any spell from the Earth domain, such as stoneskin) increases by one. This increase applies when determining level-dependent spell variables and on caster level checks. This increase stacks with other spell power abilities, such as from the hierophant prestige class." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Increase effective caster level by 1 when casting Earth-based spells.">
