  <thing id="cDFRacFoes" name="Racial Foes" description="A dwarf fighter who takes the 2nd-level racial substitution level specializes in battling his race&#146;s common enemies. He gains a +2 bonus on weapon damage rolls against orcs, goblinoids, and giants." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain +2 bonus to damage against orcs, goblinoids and giants.">
