  <thing id="cDSArcErth" name="Arcane Earthbond" description="A dwarf sorcerer who takes the 1st-level racial substitution level can draw power and support from an arcane bond he forges with the earth. Doing so takes 24 hours and uses up magic materials that cost 100 gp.\n\nThe arcane earthbond ability grants a dwarf sorcerer the Alertness feat whenever he is in contact with the ground. He also enjoys damage reduction 1/adamantine when in contact with the ground." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain Alertness and DR 1/adamantine when in contact with the ground.">
    <fieldval field="hName1" value="Forged bond"/>
