  <thing id="cGDWildEa" name="Wild Shape (Earth)" description="A goliath druid who takes the 12th-level racial substitution level can use her wild shape ability to change into an earth elemental with the same size restriction as for animal forms. The druid&#146;s maximum HD limit when taking earth elemental form (either with this ability or with her wild shape [elemental] ability gained at 16th level) is equal to her druid level +1." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Use Wild Shape to turn into an earth elemental. Cannot turn into plant.">
