  <thing id="cvGoRog2" name="Goliath Rogue" description="Although the ponderous goliath might seem ill suited to the stealthy life of a rogue, tribes rely on rogue scouts to help them survive in their hostile environments. Goliath rogues embrace their people&#146;s toughness and durability in exchange for some of the rogue&#146;s traditional agility.\n\n{b}Hit Die:{/b} d8\n\nAt 1st level, a Goliath Rogue gains Mettle of Mountains. This benefit replaces the standard rogue&#146;s 2nd-level evasion ability." compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
