  <thing id="cGRFortif" name="Fortification" description="A goliath rogue who takes the 8th-level racial substitution level develops a tough hide that allows him extra protection against potentially devastating attacks. When a critical hit or sneak attack is scored on a goliath barbarian with this substitution benefit, there is a 25% chance that the critical hit or sneak attack is negated and damage is instead rolled normally." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain a 25% chance to negate a critical hit or sneak attack.">
