  <thing id="eDwarfCrft" name="Dwarvencraft" description="Dwarvencraft items are always always masterwork quality.  Only metal or stone equipment are available in dwarvencraft quality.\n\nA dwarvencraft item is stronger and harder than a comparable masterwork item.  A dwarvencraft item&apos;s hardness increases by 2, it gains an additional 10 hit points, and gains a +2 bonus on all saving throws.  All of these effects stack with the similar bonus for magic items if the dwarvencraft item is made magical. \n\nCost (includes Masterwork cost): Weapons, +600 GP; Armor, +300 GP;" compset="Material">
